    <item>
      <title>华宝和伯克希尔哈撒韦公司即将以 30 亿美元收购 Triumph</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/warburg-berkshire-said-to-near-3-billion-deal-for-triumph</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，华平投资和伯克希尔哈撒韦公司正就收购飞机零部件和服务供应商 Triumph Group Inc. 进行深入谈判，交易金额约为 30 亿美元，其中包括债务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/warburg-berkshire-said-to-near-3-billion-deal-for-triumph</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
