      <title>美元走强超过避险需求，黄金价格持稳</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/gold-edges-higher-as-trump-tariffs-unsettle-global-markets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普对加拿大、墨西哥和中国征收关税后，世界各国准备迎接贸易战，黄金价格趋于稳定，美元飙升超过避险需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/gold-edges-higher-as-trump-tariffs-unsettle-global-markets</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Feb 2025 23:08:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普加征关税后，交易员纷纷抛售风险资产，以太币和 Memecoins 暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/crypto-bears-brunt-of-risk-off-moves-after-trump-unveils-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普对美国主要贸易伙伴征收关税的举措引发了加密货币市场的抛售，小型代币指数有望遭遇近三年来最严重的两日暴跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/crypto-bears-brunt-of-risk-off-moves-after-trump-unveils-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Feb 2025 22:20:05 GMT</pubDate>
